<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>7243</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>11243</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>萨利喜欢毛茸茸的动物玩具。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11244</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15542</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的房间里摆满了很多那样的玩具。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15543</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20206</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天，萨利的爷爷给了她一个惊喜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20207</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25539</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“萨利，我给你带了一个礼物。”爷爷说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25540</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28473</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“噢，是一只泰迪熊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28474</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32685</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>谢谢您，爷爷。”萨利惊叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32686</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37792</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不客气，萨利。”爷爷说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37793</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41913</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“爷爷，我见过黑熊和灰熊的照片，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41914</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47242</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是泰迪熊是哪种熊？”她问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47243</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53514</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爷爷开始介绍：泰迪熊有一个特别的故事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57978</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>‘泰迪’是西奥多·罗斯福的昵称，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57979</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62728</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他很多年前是美国总统。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62729</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67826</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗斯福总统很喜欢户外运动和大自然。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67884</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69678</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他喜欢打猎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69679</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76997</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然而有一次打猎时，罗斯福总统什么也没有猎到。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76998</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81431</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“应该让总统猎到点儿什么。”一个男人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81432</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87622</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果什么都没有猎到，他会很难过的。”另一个男人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87623</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90653</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我有个主意。”第三个男人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90654</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93997</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把他的计划告诉了其他人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93998</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98792</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们把一只小熊绑在了一棵树上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98793</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103324</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>总统就要放弃，打算回家了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103325</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105710</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“总统先生！总统先生！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105711</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我看到一头熊！跟我来，总统先生！”其中一个男人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112403</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117746</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他指着那只小熊说：“总统先生，那儿有一只熊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117747</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120715</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快射它！”另一个男人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120716</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125375</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>总统先生把枪瞄准了那头熊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125376</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129471</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那头熊看着罗斯福总统和枪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129472</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132415</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗斯福总统看着那头熊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132416</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135732</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我在做什么？”总统大喊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135733</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139220</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我怎么能够射杀手无寸铁的动物呢？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139221</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142458</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我不能！我不能杀死它！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142459</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147597</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天，报纸上报道了总统的故事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147643</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154592</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>题目就叫做《西奥多·罗斯福和“泰迪”熊》。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154593</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158648</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个玩具店主看到了这篇报道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158649</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167207</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他和妻子打算做一个毛茸茸的熊，并给它起名叫‘泰迪’。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167208</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170363</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>泰迪熊就这样诞生了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170364</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173181</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每个人都想得到一只。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173182</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176806</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>泰迪熊很受欢迎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176807</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181922</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“罗斯福总统是个善良的人。”萨利说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182047</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185089</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他不想杀死可怜的熊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185090</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189699</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我现在知道泰迪熊为什么这么特别了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189700</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193750</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就像您一样，爷爷！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>